# PayEvo Brand Copy

- Write in plain, practical language for Canadian SMB payroll users.
- Prefer real payroll nouns where appropriate: CRA, T4, ROE, CPP, EI, direct deposit.
- Use sentence case for general UI copy and headings.
- Use Title Case for button labels (for example: `Add Employee`, `Run Payroll`).
- Keep tone pragmatic and lightly warm; avoid enterprise jargon and jokes.
- Do not use emoji in product UI copy.
